class_name EntityDexData
## World-threat creature roster, extracted from the Periliminal.Space
## Master OmniDex. 144 creature lines (48 per faction, 8 per category ×
## 6 categories), each with up to 3 evolution stages (Stage 1 weakest,
## Stage 3 apex). Distinct from CompanionRoster (playable/collectible
## companions) — these are hostile/neutral entities encountered in the
## open world, faction-exclusive same as companions.
##
## FACTIONLESS_LINES is a hand-authored addition (not in the source doc)
## — ancient-pantheon-themed entities for players with no faction,
## pulling from public-domain mythology names (Greek/Norse/Mesopotamian/
## Canaanite). More of the pantheon list remains unused for future lines.

