	{id="WA-Q6", faction="WildlandsAscendant", category="Quantum", stages=[{name="Anpling", desc="A humanoid figure, six feet tall, with the head of a jackal — the ears are antennae of quantum reception, the nose is a detector of dimensional pathways, the eyes are pools of underworld darkness…"}, {name="Anpthresh", desc="The figure has grown to seven and a half feet, and the jackal head has developed a \"scale crown\" — a structure of gold and lapis that represents the weighing of hearts. The four arms have multiplied…"}, {}]},
	{id="WA-Q7", faction="WildlandsAscendant", category="Quantum", stages=[{name="Shuling", desc="A humanoid figure, six feet tall, that exists primarily as a shadow — the physical body is visible only in peripheral vision, a silhouette of gold-plated circuitry. The shadow-body has four arms —…"}, {name="Shuequi", desc="The figure has grown more shadow-like, seven feet tall, existing primarily in the gaps between observations. The four arms have multiplied to six, and the probability tools have become more diverse —…"}, {}]},
	{id="WA-Q8", faction="WildlandsAscendant", category="Quantum", stages=[{name="Iarephase", desc="A serpentine entity, eight feet long, with the body of a cobra composed of gold-plated circuitry. The hood is a fan of quantum probability — each scale exists in multiple states simultaneously. The…"}, {name="Iaraeg", desc="The serpent has grown to twelve feet, and the quantum hood has expanded into a \"canopy of protection\" — a complex structure of phased scales that exist in multiple defensive configurations. The four…"}, {}]},
